}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#3fdc1b79c5a3f945ba04f2f586bc844d>.
<#3fdc1b79c5a3f945ba04f2f586bc844d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
