_:b0__35767 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((11.24 69.09,26.06 69.09,26.06 55.03,11.24 55.03,11.24 69.09))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
