}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#2ed66d0ab111b917c4beacaf987171ee>.
<#2ed66d0ab111b917c4beacaf987171ee> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/617a59fa-087b-4416-83df-486b85dcb1ed>;
