_:b0__28151 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Källa: SCB, Folkhälsomyndigheten, Hälsa på lika villkor (HLV) samt Liv & H��lsa (LH), Socialstyrelsen, Nationella diabetesregistret (NDR) via Vården i Siffror."@sv;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement>.
<http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N00351> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-05-05"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Hälsa – Regionindex Kvinnor"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/GOVE>;
