<https://haninge.entryscape.net/store/7/resource/108> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#downloadURL> <https://karta.haninge.se/services/karta_open/ows?SERVICE=WFS&REQUEST=GetFeature&typeName=hojdfixar&outputFormat=kml&CRS=EPSG:3011>;
